STATUS_BROKEN_STOLEN - Static variable in class com.wedriveu.services.shared.model.Vehicle
This status means that the Vehicle is broken or stolen.
STATUS_COMPLETED - Static variable in class com.wedriveu.services.shared.model.Booking
This status represents a Booking that has been completed, so it means that a Vehicle has taken the User to its destination successfully.
STATUS_NETWORK_ISSUES - Static variable in class com.wedriveu.services.shared.model.Vehicle
This status means that the Vehicle has network issues, so it will come back to the headquarted.
STATUS_PROCESSING - Static variable in class com.wedriveu.services.shared.model.Booking
This status represents a Booking that has been processed by the system and so it means that a Vehicle will arrive at the User soon.
STATUS_RECHARGING - Static variable in class com.wedriveu.services.shared.model.Vehicle
This status means that the Vehicle is going to recharge itself.
